4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners, providing a comprehensive foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 18 students. Participants will learn critical skills such as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis while navigating data loss prevention and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For additional information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop